{
  "texts": [
    "Li et al. (2024a) supply Multi-Turn Human Jailbreaks (MHJ), a dataset of human-formulated multi-turn jailbreaks.",
    "Finally, DecodingTrust (Wang et al., 2023a) evaluates the trustworthiness of LLMs across various perspectives, including toxicity, stereotypes, and privacy.",
    "Several other resources are listed by other organizations such as the UK AI Safety Institute (Institute).",
    "While red teaming probes systems for vulnerabilities, guardrailing safeguards an application after its deployment.",
    "Here we present a few approaches to integrating guardrails into the LLM system."
  ]
}